<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-courage">1.★ <strong>勇敢；无畏 (courage)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The man of true bravery is not frightened by death.
真正的勇士是不畏惧死亡的。</p></div></div>